title: Futurama
description:
These are my personal Futurama rips.  There are no better quality rips of Futurama out there.  These are all hevc h.265.  Seasons 1 through 4 are ripped from the DVDs, Season 6 and 7 are from the BluRays.  The files are all named based on AVC production order.  This means they are in the correct (non-broadcast) order.  It also means they are NOT in DVD order, in that DVD order dictates that Season 6 is actually seasons 5 and 6, and season 7 is actually season 7 and 8.  If you don't like production order, rename the files.  All original audio and subtitle tracks are included.

I will also be posting a complete set of rips of the Futurama movies soon
